Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你没日没夜地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翻译完这些后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林和巴迪就像真正的母女一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修正一下数据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪的记忆因为她的心愿而变质了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是与白奥林相关的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  至今看到的白奥林是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林是很成功的傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不过是按照程序对依古西奥拉进行教育而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是年幼的巴迪并不能接受这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪深信她就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类实在是有着及不合理的身心构造的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们着实无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但对于同族的他来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  白奥林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他在  你就和他一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林真小气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  那塔鲁  把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁的手  好温暖好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  那是什么？  吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是丘乐酷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感到寂寞的话  我随时都会来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说定了哦  那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}阿克拉巴鲁惨剧发生后两年的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}即将在中心塔举办追悼仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}仪式上  预定会有奥之院第七席雷·西格那猊下出席进行追悼演说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}在戒备体制的配备下  以官员为首的众多与会者将在中央塔的大圆环处集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊  巴迪  很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  亏你还是依古西奥拉人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪你真笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯  紧急命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马上跟我出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基乌斯有联络  白奥林住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也不用这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是十周期一次的定期检查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,定期检查吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是坏事  跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在中心塔内的傀儡木偶专门医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去中心塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么担心了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这对白奥林来说可是好日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看一下中心塔的追悼仪式也是份不错的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西可是难得一见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也来了很多看热闹的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊  教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别光看外表  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事物的关键不在外表而是内在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  去看下警备的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有三个大队的机动巡逻部队部署在内部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正所谓人多好办事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}奥之院的雷·西格那猊下即将到达中心塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够诊断劳拉I型  对机械医来说真是幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  结果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用时间很长了  需要进行些适当的维修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在是依古西奥拉的抚养者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要调整到最佳状态哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  这就是武装警察的通常装备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主管  能到大圆环的控制室来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报告说中心塔西南南方向发生时空扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猊下显现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐标固定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  参观就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去接白奥林吧  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基乌斯应该就在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去参观仪式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了  功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  巴迪  警备的基础是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现时空漩涡  快警报！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第八区出现入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵者？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中心塔恐怖袭击发生的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  不要混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是现实  而是过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大圆环一半损坏！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快联络警备总部！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！  快撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第七区的警备中队全灭！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,侵入者的详细情报呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦政府的诸位  两年不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿克拉巴鲁的事情真是不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克丽丝蒂{\fn方正黑体_GBK}菈{\r}·利比！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是愚蠢的你们没有吸取任何教训
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅完全无视我的要求…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耐鲁兹的中队全灭！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵者正在塔内展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…那个给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥警部补？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你尽快离开中心塔  能跑多远跑多远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吗  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教官？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边  快过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  不听劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥教官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  照顾巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教官！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}我的要求和上次相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}停止对阿留多人的差别政策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}并让阿留多星从脱离联邦  承认独立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥  你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让她和帝托一起逃出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在中心塔内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够确认到巴迪的现在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  我果然应该和她在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林  你有这些侵入者的资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是帝国时代的兵器  狂战士部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(487,367)}unit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的传感器所知道范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概目标是地下动力炉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地下动力炉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想把中心塔整个炸飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪她…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我一定会救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所幸  这次有与我志同道合者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留塔人解放战线的伊兹达鲁塔助阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托  该往哪里走？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笔直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直向前就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小心上面  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒醒  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为接住你时的冲击  机能少量麻痹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能修复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  可以保证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来掉到最下层了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  往上走就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快藏起来  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉是在警戒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  有制御它们的独立单位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(447,367)}unit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  快逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会缠住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  巴迪  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴…巴迪…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那才不是白奥林！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  神经导电高分子回路也安定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(286,365)}Neuron Entangle Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子  眼下精神融合的危机算是避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林虽然是傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是拼命在保护我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这只是出于机器程序的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今也还是喜欢着白奥林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  我能问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前说过的  想再见一面的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是当时救了你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  想再见一面  好好和他道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  功  救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不…我也没…
